This wooden staff is decorated with bird carvings. While holding it, you can cause the staff to create one of the following sounds out to a range of 60 feet: a finch's chirp, a raven's caw, a duck's quack, a chicken's cluck, a goose's book, a loon's call, a turkey's gobble, a seagull's cry, an owl's hoot, or an eagle's shriek.